title: Fresh Meat Techno DJ Mix @ Stattnacht Wedding @ Stattbad @ Bunke
description:
Yay, finally a new DJ mix online. This time a set recording from one of those wonderful Stattnacht partys @ Stattbad Berlin on the evil dedicated techno Bunker floor. My slot was 1-3 before Moerbeck and Function, so I started off slow with kinda minimaly stuff, but quickly progressed to proper Techno. The party was amazing, the club was packed, the crowd was rocking, good times! Just gotta love Stattbad. Enjoy the mix icon smile Download DJ Mix: Fresh Meat @ Stattnacht @ Stattbad @ Bunker Floor 13.10.2012 (Techno)
